QuestData.Title: Salvage Operation
QuestData.Description: Between the Horde and the naga, our fleet has been decimated. We can't do anything to bring back the men who gave their lives to the sea, but sink me if I allow all of our supplies to be lost forever.$B$BSwim out to the Obsidian Breakers southwest of Highbank and retrieve our supplies from the wrecks and the ocean floor.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve 8 Recovered Supplies from Waterlogged Crates in the Obsidian Breakers.
QuestData.CompletionText: How much were you able to recover?
QuestData.RewardText: Look at all this! You were able to recover more than I thought. We can outfit a whole squad of marines with this stuff.$B$BWe have the gear. If we only had some way to bolster our numbers here in the Highlands...
